{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_01_01",
  "title": "LizNoir 01 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――長瀬麻奈が事故に遭い、帰らぬ人となってから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Mana Nagase was involved in an accident",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and passed away‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "endTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央と葵は取材を受けるため",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio and Aoi were at a certain cafe",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.333333333333333,
      "endTime": 6.333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "とある喫茶店にいた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for an interview.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.333333333333333,
      "endTime": 7.873333363305955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "endTime": 9.23680272102356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.433333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……雑誌編集の人、遅いね\n退屈だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The magazine editor is late.\nThis is boring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.433333333333334,
      "endTime": 13.701337798436482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、バックれちゃおうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ should we ditch them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9,
      "endTime": 15.90290243625641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "それはダメよ\n悪評が立つと面倒だもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can't do that.\nIt'll be a pain if we get a bad reputation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1,
      "endTime": 19.66430200890948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "プロデューサー……姫野さんが連絡してるから\n大人しく待ちなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The producer… Himeno-san is contacting them‚\nso just wait patiently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 24.645555655161544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕はいいけど\n莉央、元気がないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fine with it‚\nbut Rio‚ you seem down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.833333333333332,
      "endTime": 28.07097525155792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "――え？　そう見える？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh? Do I look like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 30.46666664282481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.666666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ\n相変わらず莉央は喫茶店が苦手みたいだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nIt seems you still don't like cafes‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.666666666666668,
      "endTime": 35.09063479105632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 35.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、葵にはバレてたのね……\nそうよ、苦手よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh You noticed‚ huh‚ Aoi…\nYeah‚ I don't like them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3,
      "endTime": 41.10643968582151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "特にこういう個人経営の小さな喫茶店はね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially these small‚ privately owned cafes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3,
      "endTime": 44.811927413940424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "理由はやっぱり昔のこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is the reason because of that thing from the past?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1,
      "endTime": 47.153673434257506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 47.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、葵も知ってるでしょ\n面白い話じゃないわ、もうその話はやめましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. You know about it‚ Aoi.\nIt's not a fun story. Let's not talk about it anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.36666666666667,
      "endTime": 54.846621195475265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ただのヒマつぶしだよ\n霧子が戻るまででいいからさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just trying to kill time.\nJust until Kiriko gets back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 59.35750563939414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 59.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "それに少なくとも\n僕には聞く権利はあるんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ at the very least‚\ndon't I have the right to ask?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 63.88333352406819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 64.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 64.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 65.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ、分かったわよ\n絶対、他の人には内緒よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh Fine.\nYou absolutely can't tell anyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 71.13974705344688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 71.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "この発展途上の胸にかけて誓うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I swear on my still-developing chest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 74.03333342870076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――とん、と葵は自分の胸を軽く叩いた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Aoi lightly tapped his own chest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 77.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 77.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その様子を見て、莉央はくすりと微笑した",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing that‚ Rio let out a small chuckle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 79.97333346033484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "知ってると思うけど\n私の実家は、小さな喫茶店を経営しててね――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You probably already know‚\nbut my family runs a small cafe――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 86.01666685740153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 87
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 87
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、行ってくるわ、お母さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going now‚ Mom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 90.69789110819498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "頑張ってね、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good luck‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9,
      "endTime": 92.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それから東京は人が多いから気を付けて歩くのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And be careful walking around in Tokyo‚ it's crowded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 96.98387737274169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 97.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
